Dolce & Gabbana to Open E-Commerce Site Tomorrow With Yoox

-- B y   A n d r e w   R o b e r t s
-- 
2011-07-12T16:18:25Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-07-12/dolce-gabbana-to-open-e-commerce-site-tomorrow-with-yoox.html
Dolce & Gabbana , an Italian fashion
company, said it will open an e-commerce site tomorrow with
online retailer  Yoox SpA. (YOOX)   The site will sell men’s and women’s clothing and
accessories and will be available in seven languages, Milan-
based Dolce & Gabbana said today in a statement. Delivery will
be free for the first three months.  A Chinese version of the store, serving 400 cities in the
Asian country, will follow on Aug. 8, the company said.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Andrew Roberts in Paris at 
 aroberts36@bloomberg.net .  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Celeste Perri at   cperri@bloomberg.net  